<br>
The <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> only</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> hard part is finding the mob up. For that, you can park a tracker north of the amy temple when the plane is clear, and log him in regularly. There is only one wanderer up there, and he does not see through invis. For what it's worth, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Cazic Thule doesn't matter to you much</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<br>
<br>
If you see the mob up:<br>
<br>
- Buff up, FD puller zone in, puller FD and tell people when to zone. Then everyone zone, train mobs to west wall, fight there, repeat until no more mobs.<br>
<br>
- Work your way north and clear all mobs until no mobs are between you and the Amy temple.<br>
<br>
- Have a cleric or other DA-able person pull the whole temple at once, and have the cleric or one other person run the mobs around in a big circle. The wraith won't follow if done right. The puller shouldn't get too near the wraith.<br>
<br>
- Have the main puller pull the wraith meanwhile (important that the wraith doesn't get into the AE from the mobs).<br>
<br>
- Kill shissar.<br>
<br>
- Loot stuff.<br>
<br>
- /dance<br>
